	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sat, Dec 1st 3:32 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>This staff dropped for our group last night.&nbsp;&nbsp;It came off a named cube (one of the lower level cubes that sit together behind Oct Velic... Ortho Velic or Polhidral Velic I believe are their names).  As with most weapons that drop off cubes, you can see this thing sitting inside while you fight it.  Granted it could be one of a few different staves but a tip-off that you are going to get this weapon to drop is if the cube you are fighting mysteriously has a fire dmg shield.  Nice weapon, but as it says above it IS No Drop.<br><br>Jaxphar (RZ)<br>55 Erudite Revenant<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
